In  fact,  Mr.  Chairman,  we  had  this  past  summer  a  very,  very 
constructive  meeting  and  a  3-day  session  in  your  state  of  Hawaii, 
which I must say was most enjoyable. 

I  pledge  that  I  do  bring  a  strong  commitment  to  this  system, 
which  is  reinforced  through  my  exposure  to  the  good  work  of  the 
corporation that it has accomplished, and I would like to continue, 
Mr. Chairman and Members of the Committee, to help make a con-
tribution  to  CPB’s  quest  for  excellence.  We  are  certainly  on  our 
