Jewish News (5/89). 
‘‘Dodd  &  Weicker  Should  Stop  Meddling  In  The  Israel  Issue,’’  Letter  to  Editor, 
New Haven Register (04/88). 

17.  Please  identify  each  instance  in  which  you  have  testified  orally  or  in  writing 
before  Congress  in  a  governmental  or  non-governmental  capacity  and  specify  the 
date and subject matter of each testimony. 

03/21/07  Testimony as Chairman of CPB Board of Directors, Subcommittee on Labor, Health 

and Human Services, Education and Related Agencies, U.S. House Committee on 
Appropriations. 

11/04/03  Confirmation hearing for appointment to CPB Board Senate Committee on Com-

merce, Science and Transportation. 

